        <summary>Is this connected to Bondee's Barnyard?</summary>
        <div>Both games share the same developer (Mitnick's team). There's a subtle connection — a Funtime Freddy element is visible at the start of Welcome to Fredbear's — but the game works as a standalone experience with its own story.</div>
